            "title": "Direitos das crian\u00e7as e pr\u00e1tica pedag\u00f3gica : implica\u00e7\u00f5es sobre a constru\u00e7\u00e3o do conhecimento social em sala de aula",
            "abstract": [
                "This book presents theoretical and practical reflections on the construction of social knowledge in the light of Genetic Epistemology. Children's rights, as an important social theme present in school curricula, was the main focus of the discussions to be presented here, through the report of a pedagogical intervention that sought to know, evaluate and collaborate for the construction of social notions more elaborated by students of the Elementary School I. The importance of teachers working with the construction of social knowledge in the classroom is highlighted, and it brings contributions as it draws attention to active, fruitful and colluding ways with child development, of thinking in an educational context , truly, constructivist, concerned with the formation of citizen children, in essence, critical, autonomous and reflective",
                "Este livro apresenta reflex\u00f5es te\u00f3ricas e pr\u00e1ticas sobre a constru\u00e7\u00e3o do conhecimento social \u00e0 luz da Epistemologia Gen\u00e9tica. Os direitos das crian\u00e7as, enquanto importante tem\u00e1tica social presente nos curr\u00edculos escolares, foi o enfoque principal das discuss\u00f5es a serem aqui apresentadas , atrav\u00e9s do relato de uma interven\u00e7\u00e3o pedag\u00f3gica que buscou conhecer, avaliar e colaborar para a constru\u00e7\u00e3o de no\u00e7\u00f5es sociais mais elaboradas por alunos do Ensino Fundamental I. Destaca-se a relev\u00e2ncia dos docentes trabalharem com a constru\u00e7\u00e3o do conhecimento social em sala de aula, e traz contribui\u00e7\u00f5es \u00e0 medida que chama aten\u00e7\u00e3o para formas ativas, prof\u00edcuas e coniventes com o desenvolvimento infantil, de se pensar em um contexto educativo, verdadeiramente, construtivista, preocupado com a forma\u00e7\u00e3o de crian\u00e7as cidad\u00e3s, na ess\u00eancia, cr\u00edticas, aut\u00f4nomas e reflexivas"
